data.description: Don't miss out on this great ranch in a great location with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms. Home includes an open living room, dining room and kitchen area. Just off the dining room is a three season room to enjoy Michigan warm seasons. The basement is partially completed and ready for you to put your design around the welcoming fireplace. The backyard is fenced in with an amazing custom built small barn/shed. The barn/shed has a clean slate inside just waiting for your personal touch. Call today for a private showing.
